    <title>dnmp 为PHP 安装扩展</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2019/05/29/dnmp-%E4%B8%BAPHP-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%89%A9%E5%B1%95/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2019/05/29/dnmp-为PHP-安装扩展/</id>
    <published>2019-05-29T14:24:55.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-05-29T14:34:36.701Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>本地使用 dnmp 作为开发环境, 结果某一个项目使用的环境为 php56, 连接数据库使用的 mysql_connect, 当服务启动起来后,<br>缺少mysql extension , 造成无法运行. </p><p>解决办法:</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker exec -it dnmp_php56_1 /bin/bash</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>进入镜像后, 运行<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker-php-ext-install mysql</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>然后在php.ini 文件中 , 添加</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[Mysql]</span><br><span class="line">mysql.allow_local_infile = On</span><br><span class="line">mysql.allow_persistent = On</span><br><span class="line">mysql.cache_size = 2000</span><br><span class="line">mysql.connect_timeout = 60</span><br><span class="line">mysql.default_host = &quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">mysql.default_password = &quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">mysql.default_port = &quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">mysql.default_socket = &quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">mysql.default_user = &quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">mysql.max_links = -1</span><br><span class="line">mysql.max_persistent = -1</span><br><span class="line">mysql.trace_mode = Off</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>重启 php56, nginx 镜像.<br>可以在根目录执行 </p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker-compose restart</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>或者<br><code>`</code><br>docker container restart containerid</p>]]></content>
    
